items.description:
facialized: a new LoRA for facials on women

LoRA to generate photo-realistic images of women with cum on their face.

Include in your prompt <lora:facialized:1>, cum, facial.You might want to include in your negative prompt cum on breasts, cum on body.

The model works best with low steps and CFG, I get good results with 10 steps and a CFG of 3 or 4.

I am open to advice/help to improve this LoRA. If you are willing to help, you can send me a mail at the mail address at the end of this description.

Training methodology below.

Know issues with the model

As rightly noted by some comments, the model is still imperfect. Here is a list of a few issues I found, along with ways to circumvent them when possible.
I will share tags present in the training dataset that might help you circumvent some of these issues in the format the tag in question [number of images out of 2676 that were associated with this tag]. For example smiling at camera [486] means that 486 images in the dataset (composed of 2676 images in total) had the tag smiling at camera.

Cum on the body / torso

Most of the generated images depict women with cum on their body / torso / breasts. It is currently hard to remove it and ensure that cum only appears on the face.

Here are some tags present in the training dataset that might help you with this issue:

  • cum on breasts [195]

  • cum on body [472]

  • cum on clothes [10]

Bad eyes

The model might generate faces with non-symmetrical eyes or ill-formed eyes. You can try to alleviate this by using tags such as:

  • symmetric eyes

  • same color eyes

  • bad eyes (negative prompt)

  • strange eyes (negative prompt)

These tags do not appear in the training data but help the underlying stable diffusion checkpoint generating correct faces.

Training methodology explained

Disclaimer: this is my first time making a LoRA and I am more than open to advice to improve it! I am detailing my methodology below, if you have any idea on how to improve it please feel free to comment.

Dataset

The full dataset is composed of 2676 images, hand-picked from one source. Their quality varies greatly, but nearly all of them show a unique women with cum on her face. Some outliers show 2 women (~10 images).

The image sizes are very disparate, I am reproducing here a count of the number of images for each resolution that has 10 or more images (there are 1454 different resolutions in the whole dataset).

Training

I used https://colab.research.google.com/github/hollowstrawberry/kohya-colab/blob/main/Lora_Trainer.ipynb to train the LoRA. The training model was sd-v1-5-pruned-noema-fp16.safetensors. Tags are automatically shuffled and there is no activation tags (activation_tags set to 0).

Due to the size of the dataset, each image is only repeated once (i.e., no repetition). I used 5 epochs, with a batch size of 2. The UNet learning rate was set to 5e-4. The LoRA network dimension was set to 32, and the network alpha to 16.

Further notes on other tentatives

I tried to manually filter images to only include "nice" images:

  • high enough resolution and quality

  • no cum on body

  • "pretty" women (according to my taste)

I filtered down the dataset to 1170 images, re-trained a LoRA, but the resulting model is clearly under-performing. I even have hard times trying make cum appear on the generated images with this model.

I tried different LoRA network dimension and alpha dimension ((16, 8), (32, 16) and (64, 32)), but the best performing one seems to be the (32, 16).

Should be compatible with most modern realism models, and should potentially work with other character/person LoRAs

  • What's the + for?

    • Just an easy way to indicate the dataset image for this particular LORA was based off a minimum of 1024px+ quality source images with the LORA trained at 1024,1024 (I may go higher in the future if I can get a properly working configuration).

    • For the most part, you can start with higher base resolutions to capture more details and/or generate higher quality outputs. See some of the gallery examples.

    • You don't have to gen at high resolution, low res generations will be better quality as well.

  • LoRA weight: 1

  • 40+ Steps: For better photoreal shots

  • Take control: ControlNet is your friend.

    • Tile pre-sample is good for extreme close ups

    • I often use segmentation for my generations now

  • Inpaint: Face details? ~.3 - .45 denoise

🚀Upscaling🚀

  • Though I didn't use it for the base gallery examples, it should still work.

  • Try the Ultimate SD upscale script!

  • Sometimes I just send it to Ultimate SD upscale after a quick render and run 2x at a scale of two.

  • Ultimate SD upscale script used @ ~.15 - .4 denoising using 8x NMKD Faces or 4X UltraSharp redraw upscalers.

🗒️Side Notes🗒️

  • This + series is something new, let me know if I should take the extra time it takes to create these type of LoRAs or just stick with the regular quality.

  • Help me help you: Leave a review if you've used this LoRA.

  • Most of my gens are not voodoo or outside of workflows I've indicated here or in my other posts.

    • In other words: Leave a comment if you are having issues getting good output, I'll try to respond with some suggestions.

Anemone

anemone is one of my first trained model, at first I wasn't satisfied with the results I got, then some time ago I watched some old anime and movies (especially Kill Bill movie LOL), and then an idea occurred to me to retrain, by adding some images in the existing dataset.
Dataset has been preprocessed using Aspect Ratio Bucketing Tool so that it can be converted to latents and trained at non-square resolutions.

Legal & Risk

In principle, I do not support the use of this model to generate any adult content. When using this model, users must abide by laws and regulations, and do not infringe other people's reputation, privacy or portrait rights.

Changelogs

  • v1.0-fp16: added fp16 (no EMA) model

Who find this model perfect

  • LoRA/LoCon/LyCORIS user who are looking for a compatible checkpoint

  • Creative prompters

Usage

  • Almost compatible with all sampling methods available, but Euler a and DPM++ SDE Karras are my recommendation

  • Use at least 20 sampling steps, more than 40 is not giving any improvement

  • CFG: 4.5-7

  • Less complicated, short negative prompts are better

  • Preffered VAE

If using Hires:

  • Hires step: 10-20 steps

  • R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6b, if you're prefer Latent upscaler, use Latent (nearest-exact)

Ma-Mian skirt, or Horse-Face skirt, is one of the traditional Chinese clothing, originated in China about 1,000 years ago during the Song Dynasty, and gained popularity 600 years ago during the Ming Dynasty, when it was the predominant clothing of Han Chinese women. It's a kind of gorgeous and neat skirt that can be worn with either a long or short shirt.

Trigger word: "light green/red/blue/yellow/purple long skirt" ,"birds/flowers/leaf print" , anyway, use your imagination to edit them as much as possible. And you can increase the weight of the trigger words appropriately.

Don't set lora's weight too high

Overview

A complex triple-merging method. Mainly focusing on Sci-Fantasy boys (but still works with girls and general arts) with the best intricate every single detail.

Recommended Textual Inversion Embeddings

Gender Slider, deformityv6, EasyNegative, Simplenegative, bad-hands-5, Unspeakable-Horrors-Composition-4v.

DDetailer, ADetailer, Tiled Diffusion & VAE, Ultimate SD Upscale

Absurdres, Intricate Details, Masterpiece, Best Quality, High Resolution, 8k

  • Size: 512x768 (default - it might not result well if you set it up below this ratio)

  • Sampling method: Euler a, DPM++ 2M Karras, DPM++ 2M alt Karras, DPM++ SDE Karras, DPM++ 2M SDE Karras,

items.name: Abba - Hentai University
items.description:
This is a LoRA for the character Abba, from Hentai University a game by Noodle Jacuzzi.

Abba's art is from the artist Silver Radish, the set -

Inma Shuurai -Gotsukute Kowakute Chotto Kawaii Doero Kasshoku Inma ♀ Hen-

I've been working my way through making these for all the characters currently in the game, and sharing them in the Discord for HU, but figured I should also put them up here.

In general, I'm working from pretty limited image sets, so expect the results to be a bit wonky at times.

I recommend a weight of around 0.5, possibly lower depending if you're combining the character LoRA with other styles/costumes/etc. along with tagging some defining characteristics of the character you're generating. Higher than that can really push the artist's original style, and may cause you issues.

All characters I train have a "character tag" added into the set to help generate them fairly reliably.

Recommended LoRA Weight - 0.5 for fairly flexible, higher if you want more of the original artist's style, lower if it doesn't play nice with other loras.

Character tag - HUAbba
Recommended tags - horns, dark skin, white hair, long hair, demon wings, large breasts, toned, muscular female, pointy ears,

Sometimes sharp teeth can work, but as always, the AI is iffy about chompers, so use at your own risk.

I've got quite a backlog of these made up already, so I'll be uploading them on and off.

items.name: Herta | Honkai: Star Rail LoRA
items.description:
CC License

yeah yeah I know that this "Kuru Kuru~" doll that Mihoyo gave us which the internet loves so much probably has more than 10 LoRAs posted online but you know what they say

"You can never be spammed with too many of Herta's Kuru Kurus"

so with that here I am to post another Herta LoRA that was made with a collection of official images and fan art posted of her online!

Recommended Weight

Always 1.0 by itself and 0.8-0.7 if you're mixing it with other LORAs (I prefer to have the character LoRA be at 1.0 while the concept and style LoRAs are lowered in strength but you do you)

Compatibility

Trained on the "final pruned" NAI model, so it's pretty much compatible with every NAI based Anime model mix that you can find on the internet (which is pretty much all of them)

Trigger Tokens

regherta will be the token needed for her normal look, you can easily get her look as long as if you use that trigger token along with these additional tags

"doll joints, bangs, beret, black headwear, dress, white dress, hair flower, hair ornament, long hair, long sleeves, purple eyes, purple flower, sailor collar, brown hair, grey hair, chain, choker"

and if you want to change her hair or put her into different outfits like I did with the obvious preview images... don't use the keep token, up the strength, and mostly cherry pick with the outfit outputs, not sure why but Herta's choker really loved this LoRA and got baked in pretty hard so you're going to have to hope with putting it in negative prompts and cherry picking your final outputs, it works but be prepared to pass through many seeds. (I really don't like it when my LoRAs do that especially when I'm using the 8 network rank baking method so I might update this LORA if there's some stuff I can do to fix it, the LoRA will still work fine with multiple LORAs [concept/style] like it did in the obvious preview image)

Support

Just like the "support section" of many "BIG" LoRA posters here, I'll be happy enough if you support me on one of my platforms, Pixiv and Twitter for my posted works while Ko-Fi/Fiverr/Patreon can be visited to support me financially I'll do the provided jobs for you on Fiverr and Ko-Fi/Patreon are there with early releases of mixes or LoRAs because I take a long ass time to get preview images, thanks a lot if you support me o/

items.name: JAV Rina_石原○奈
items.description:
Rina is my favorite JAV actress of all time and I think her acting skills and performances during her time in the Attackers were the greatest in all of JAV history. It took me some time to finish this Lora because her images are really limited on the internet... But now here it is, though the result is not really satisfying, that is the best I can do for now, cheers.

I've updated my training method for better compatibility, and tuneability. It is now less overcooked compared to old ones.

If you want her to smile, just add "smile" to the prompt.

If you want a smile with teeth, just add "smile, teeth" to the prompt.

If you want a smile but a closed mouth, "smile, (closed mouth:1.5)" to the prompt and "teeth, open mouth" to the negative prompt.

I've also tested its tunability with hairstyles.

See all of these comparisons in the gallery.

For how I train LORAs, see description of JAV Anzai_RI○N | Stable Diffusion LORA | Civitai

Must turn on Hires.fix

Hires steps:17, denoising:0.5+

Use DPM++ 2M Karras or DPM++ SDE Karras

Strength: 0.5-0.9

She might look like someone from real life, but she is not what you think. She is a totally fictional character.

Checkpoint used for samples: Basil Mix, kanpiromix, majicMIX realistic and henmixreal

VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000 from StabilityAI

items.name: Alyx Vance
items.description:
This is a model of Alyx Vance from Half Life 2. It is fairly versatile, and should be able to depict her in a variety of styles, poses, and clothing.

Issues:

  • Kinda breaks over 768x768 if not using high-res fix.

  • Her grey Black Mesa sweater shows up very often even if not specified. I can fix this by finding and training the model on a few nude versions of Alyx, I guess. For now you can somewhat mitigate it by putting "gray / grey shirt" in the negative prompt.

  • Tends to generate her with a sweater, jacket or hoodie even if specified otherwise.

  • AND sections of prompts can be fairly strong sometimes, you can decrease their weights with (brackets:)

  • Occasional lazy eye. No idea how to fix.

  • Her hair can be shaped as though she is wearing an invisible headband.

  • Her necklace can have two laces or no lace.

  • It likes to give her a crop top. Not really a problem tbh, it looks cool. :>

Enjoy! Eli Vance will be coming soon. :)

items.description:
still life,Oil paintings,Flowers, fruit,静物Lora

重要:Lora名字被我修改了<lora:KK_still_life_v2:1>,

复制tag的时候,记得把Lora名字修改过来.<lora:still_life_v3:1>

Important: I have changed Lora's name to <lora:KK_still_life_v2:1>.

When copying the tag, remember to change Lora's name over. <lora:still_life_v3:1>

____________________________________________________________________

在测试这个Lora的时候,非常惊喜,好多模型都可以得到很好的展现,

个人比较喜欢用写实的模型来生成静物图片,当然漫画风格的生成也不错,

我测试了十几个模型,基本没有出现崩坏的情况,你也可以自行尝试一下不同的模型,

V1版本传送门:https://civitai.com/models/56374/ins-stylestill-lifesimple-background

V2版本:

这个版本我用了不同的图片训练集,生成出来的物品也非常丰富,

之所以没有合并在一起发布,我觉得这个Lora生成的风格和v1还是有很大不同,

使用说明:

触发词:still_life

Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras or Dpm++SDE
CFG: 5-9, steps: 30-50

分辨率建议:512或者768,需要丰富的细节,建议超分,

添加Lora+still life就能生成漂亮的静物画,甚至不需要画质描述词,就是这么不讲道理.

当然也可以添加一些画质和光影的描述词:(masterpiece),(best quality),8k, detailed, ultra detail, soothing tones, muted colors, nature lights,realistic ,blurry, solo focus,等,可以自由发挥,

也可以添加:scratch, squiggly, old,vintage,等复古旧物的描述,

可以参考我发布的图片上的描述信息.

有问题可以留言.由于训练集有些图片水印没有去干净,偶尔会生成一些带水印的,影响不大,20张里可能会有一张,

有时间再升级版本,把水印去干净.

_____________________________________________________________________________

still life, Oil paintings, Flowers, fruit, still life Lora

When testing this Lora, I was very surprised by how well many models could be represented.

Personally, I prefer to use realistic models to generate still life images, but of course caricature style generation is also good.

I have tested about a dozen models and there is basically no crashing, you can also try different models yourself.

V1 version portal:https://civitai.com/models/56374/ins-stylestill-lifesimple-background

Version V2.

I used a different image training set for this version, and the resulting items are very rich.

The reason why I didn't combine them in one release is that I think the style of Lora generation is still very different from v1.

Instructions for use.

Trigger word: still_life

Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras or Dpm++SDE

CFG: 5-9, steps: 30-50

Resolution recommended: 512 or 768, rich detail required, superscoring recommended.

Adding Lora+still life will produce beautiful still life paintings without even needing a quality descriptor, it's that unreasonable.

Of course you can also add some descriptors for quality and light: (masterpiece), (best quality), 8k, detailed, ultra detail, soothing tones, muted colours, nature lights, realistic ,blurry. solo focus, etc., feel free to play around with it.

You can also add: scratch, squiggly, old, vintage, and other vintage descriptions.

Please refer to the descriptions on the pictures I have posted.

If you have any questions, please leave a comment. As some of the images in the training set are not watermarked properly, some of them are generated occasionally with a watermark, but it does not matter much, there may be one out of 20.

I will update the version to remove the watermark when I have time.

__________________________________________________________________________

PS:不知道为啥我传的图片不能自动识别图片参数信息,还要手动添加,好麻烦,我把图片参数信息全部添加到正面描述中了,就这样将就看吧.

(复制全部参数然后点小箭头就可以把参数添加进SD webui中了)

复制全部参数然后点小箭头就可以把参数添加进SD webui中了

items.name: Marianna Rothen Style
items.description:
Marianna Rothen is a contemporary photographer and visual artist known for her cinematic and evocative photographic works.

Her style can be described as nostalgic, dreamlike, and imbued with a sense of mystery. Rothen often creates narratives within her photographs, exploring themes of identity, femininity, and the complexities of human relationships.

Her images often evoke a sense of retro aesthetics, drawing inspiration from vintage fashion, classic cinema, and mid-20th century Americana. Rothen's use of color, lighting, and composition adds a cinematic quality to her photographs, capturing moments frozen in time.

She frequently employs self-portraiture and features female figures as central subjects in her work, inviting viewers to reflect on notions of beauty, intimacy, and the power dynamics within relationships.

Rothen's photographs possess a subtle tension and underlying narrative, inviting viewers to engage with her carefully crafted visual storytelling. Her images often blur the line between reality and fiction, creating a sense of ambiguity and intrigue.

Through her work, Rothen explores themes of memory, desire, and the constructed nature of identity. Her photographs provoke introspection and contemplation, encouraging viewers to question societal norms and reflect on their own experiences.

Marianna Rothen's artistic vision and narrative-driven photography have garnered critical acclaim and exhibitions in galleries and museums worldwide. Her evocative imagery continues to captivate audiences, drawing them into her introspective and visually compelling world.

items.description:
LoRA model of Tsubasa Ibuki (伊吹翼) from media-mix project THE IDOLM@STER MILLION LIVE! (アイドルマスターミリオンライブ！).

The trigger word is tsubasa ibuki (million live). The LoRA weight of samples is 0.8-0.85; you can also try other weights. The greater the weight, the closer the character style is to the game card of THE IDOLM@STER MILLION LIVE! THEATER DAYS (ミリシタ) and the new tachie drawn after the release of the game.

Note: I load my LoRA model through the additional network WebUI plugin, so the prompt of sample illustrations don't contain <lora:XXX:X> tag.

I'll appreciate it if you're willing to use this LoRA model and share AI arts to other people. My models and illustrations are free for everyone, and if you like them, please support me at Patreon or 爱发电.

————————————

跨媒体企划《偶像大师 百万现场》的角色伊吹翼的LoRA模型

模型的触发词为 tsubasa ibuki (million live)。示例图的LoRA权重为0.8-0.85，您也可以尝试其他权重值。权重越大，角色风格越接近游戏《偶像大师 百万现场 剧场时光》（MLTD）游戏卡面以及该游戏发行后新绘制的立绘
